'''Rylca''' was a cure for the [[krytos virus]] formed by growing certain [[Bacta/Legends|bacta]] ingredients in a [[ryll kor]] enriched environment. It was developed by the [[Vratix/Legends|Vratix]] [[verachen]] [[Qlaern Hirf]] for the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] in [[7 ABY/Legends|7 ABY]] to cure the krytos plague outburst on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. [[Alderaan Biotics]] was a large rylca manufacturer.<ref name="TKT">''[[X-Wing: The Krytos Trap]]''</ref>

